FBIS3-34776 "drnes031_s_94004" FBIS-NES-94-031 Document Type:Daily Report 15 Feb 1994 SOUTH ASIA Iran Velayati Appoints First Deputy Foreign Minister LD1402140294 Tehran IRNA in English 1323 GMT 14 Feb 94 LD1402140294 Tehran IRNA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Tehran, Feb. 14, IRNA -- Iran's Foreign Minister 'Ali Akbar Velayati here Monday appointed Mohammad Hashemi as his first deputy. Hashemi has served as head of the Islamic Republic of Iran Broadcasting (IRIB) for the past 13 years. In a decree on Sunday, leader of the Islamic revolution Ayatollah 'Ali Khamene'i appointed former Islamic Guidance Minister 'Ali Larijani as the new IRIB head.
